resources.description: Based on the data of events of magnitude Ms ≥ 5.0 and shallow or moderate focal depth occurred between 1990 and 2010, which is collected by 13 broadband digital stations deployed in Southern China area and surrounding areas, 470 generated Rayleigh waves and Love waves can be accessed by applying the technique of matches filter frequency time analysis.
resources.name: Love and Rayleigh Wave Tomography of Crustal Structure in Southern
